  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个测试覆盖率的饼图，展示四个核心层的覆盖率对比。标题就叫「テストカバレッジ分布」吧，用日文比较贴近我们的项目文档风格。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pie chart",
        "title: テストカバレッジ分布"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，四个层具体是哪几个？我需要确认一下命名和对应的百分比，这样饼图的分区才能准确反映数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "four layers",
        "percentage values"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "四个层分别是：Domain Layer 96%，Application Layer 100%，Infrastructure 84%，Presentation 100%。Application和Presentation都达到了满分，Infrastructure相对薄弱一些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Layer (96%)",
        "Application Layer (100%)",
        "Infrastructure (84%)",
        "Presentation (100%)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以分区大小应该是：Application Layer 和 Presentation 并列最大，都是100；Domain Layer 96 稍小一点；Infrastructure 84 最小。这个比例关系对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application Layer (100)",
        "Presentation (100)",
        "Domain Layer (96)",
        "Infrastructure (84)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，比例正确。不过标签上最好把百分比也带上，比如写成「Domain Layer (96%)」这种格式，一眼就能看出具体数值。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Layer (96%)",
        "Application Layer (100%)",
        "Infrastructure (84%)",
        "Presentation (100%)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我按这个格式来画。标题加上📊图标，四个层分别标注为 Domain Layer (96%)、Application Layer (100%)、Infrastructure (84%)、Presentation (100%)，数值对应96、100、84、100。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pie title \"📊 テストカバレッジ分布\"",
        "Domain Layer (96%) : 96",
        "Application Layer (100%) : 100",
        "Infrastructure (84%) : 84",
        "Presentation (100%) : 100"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等一下，Infrastructure 的标签好像和其他层不太一致——其他层都有「Layer」后缀，这个直接写「Infrastructure」会显得突兀。改成「Infrastructure Layer (84%)」会不会更统一？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure (84%)",
        "Infrastructure Layer (84%)"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确实，统一性很重要。不过我们项目里 Infrastructure 通常作为独立术语使用，不加「Layer」反而更符合惯例。如果坚持统一，我可以调整，但建议保持现状。你觉得呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure",
        "Infrastructure Layer",
        "naming convention"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "你说得对，Infrastructure 确实习惯单独用。那保持「Infrastructure (84%)」吧，其他的也不动。最终就是：Domain Layer (96%)、Application Layer (100%)、Infrastructure (84%)、Presentation (100%)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Layer (96%)",
        "Application Layer (100%)",
        "Infrastructure (84%)",
        "Presentation (100%)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认定稿。饼图标题「📊 テストカバレッジ分布」，四个分区按最终确认的标签和数值呈现，100%的两个层并列最大，清晰展示测试覆盖分布。",
